---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Culture" description="Culture — K-drama, K-pop, beauty, language, and Korean lifestyle for Singaporeans. The Hansang.">

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <div class="page-header-korean" lang="ko" aria-hidden="true">문화</div>
      <h1>Culture</h1>
      <p class="page-header-desc">K-drama deep dives, K-pop culture, Korean beauty picks, language tips, and the lifestyle stories that connect Singapore to Korea.</p>
      <p class="page-header-count">6 articles</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <a href="/culture/k-drama-restaurant-guide" class="featured-article" aria-label="Featured: The K-Drama Restaurant Guide">
    <article class="featured-article-inner">
      <div class="featured-article-image">[ featured photograph ]</div>
      <span class="featured-article-label">Featured</span>
      <h2 class="featured-article-title">The K-Drama Restaurant Guide: Every Real Restaurant from Your Favourite Shows</h2>
      <p class="featured-article-excerpt">From the pojangmacha in My Love from the Star to the restaurant in Itaewon Class, we tracked down the real locations and tell you which ones are actually worth visiting.</p>
      <div class="featured-article-meta">March 2026 &middot; 10 min read</div>
    </article>
  </a>

  <div class="filter-bar" role="toolbar" aria-label="Filter articles by topic">
    <div class="filter-bar-inner">
      <span class="filter-label">Filter</span>
      <ul class="filter-tags" role="list">
        <li><button type="button" class="active" aria-pressed="true">All</button></li>
        <li><button type="button" aria-pressed="false">K-Drama</button></li>
        <li><button type="button" aria-pressed="false">K-Pop</button></li>
        <li><button type="button" aria-pressed="false">Beauty</button></li>
        <li><button type="button" aria-pressed="false">Language</button></li>
        <li><button type="button" aria-pressed="false">Lifestyle</button></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="article-list" aria-label="Articles">
    <div class="article-grid">
      <a href="/culture/k-drama-restaurant-guide" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">K-Drama</div><h3 class="article-card-title">The K-Drama Restaurant Guide: Real Restaurants from Your Favourite Shows</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">We visited every real restaurant featured in recent K-dramas. Here is which ones are worth the trip.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Mar 22, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/culture/korean-beauty-routine-singapore" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">Beauty</div><h3 class="article-card-title">The 10-Step Korean Skincare Routine, Adapted for Singapore Weather</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">Humidity changes everything. How to adapt the Korean skincare routine for tropical skin without breaking the bank.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Mar 18, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/culture/korean-phrases-ordering-food" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">Language</div><h3 class="article-card-title">20 Korean Phrases You Need for Ordering Food in Korea</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">From "how much is this" to "no spice please" to "one more beer." The survival Korean you actually need at restaurants.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Mar 14, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/culture/kpop-cafe-culture-seoul" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">K-Pop</div><h3 class="article-card-title">K-Pop Cafe Culture in Seoul: Birthday Cafes and Cupsleeve Events</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">The cupsleeve event is a uniquely Korean fan culture phenomenon. Here is how it works and where to find them.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Mar 10, 2026</div></a>
      <div class="ad-slot" role="complementary" aria-label="Advertisement"><span class="ad-slot-label">Supported by</span><div class="ad-slot-placeholder">[ ad placement &middot; 728 &times; 90 ]</div></div>
      <a href="/culture/korean-drinking-culture" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">Lifestyle</div><h3 class="article-card-title">Korean Drinking Culture Explained: Soju Etiquette, Anju, and the Rules</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">Pour with two hands, never pour your own, and always turn away from elders. The unwritten rules of Korean drinking.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Mar 6, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/culture/best-k-dramas-food-lovers" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">K-Drama</div><h3 class="article-card-title">8 K-Dramas Every Food Lover Should Watch</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">Let's Eat, Wok of Love, and six more shows that will make you hungry and teach you about Korean food culture.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Feb 28, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/culture/where-to-buy-korean-beauty-singapore" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">Beauty</div><h3 class="article-card-title">Where to Buy Korean Beauty Products in Singapore</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">From Olive Young dupes at Watsons to the dedicated K-beauty stores in Bugis and Orchard. A price comparison guide.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Feb 22, 2026</div></a>
      <a href="/culture/korean-table-manners" class="article-card"><div class="article-card-image">[ photo ]</div><div class="article-card-pillar">Lifestyle</div><h3 class="article-card-title">Korean Table Manners: What Singaporeans Get Wrong</h3><p class="article-card-excerpt">Chopsticks upright in rice, lifting your bowl, and other habits that feel normal to us but read differently in Korea.</p><div class="article-card-meta">Feb 16, 2026</div></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <nav class="pagination" aria-label="Page navigation">
    <span class="prev disabled" aria-hidden="true">&larr; Prev</span>
    <a href="#" class="active" aria-current="page" aria-label="Page 1">1</a>
    <a href="#" aria-label="Page 2">2</a>
    <a href="#" class="next" aria-label="Next page">Next &rarr;</a>
  </nav>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { padding: 64px 48px 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.1s both; }
  .page-header-inner { max-width: 640px; }
  .page-header-korean { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 56px; font-weight: 200; line-height: 1; color: var(--stone); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .page-header h1 { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 44px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .page-header-desc { font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .page-header-count { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); }
  .featured-article { display: block; padding: 0 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink); animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.15s both; transition: background 0.2s; }
  .featured-article:hover { background: var(--linen); }
  .featured-article-inner { padding: 40px 0; }
  .featured-article-image { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; background: var(--stone); margin-bottom: 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 0.08em; overflow: hidden; }
  .featured-article-label { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); border: 1px solid var(--stone); padding: 2px 8px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .featured-article-title { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 12px; text-wrap: balance; max-width: 720px; }
  .featured-article-excerpt { font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .featured-article-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .filter-bar { padding: 0 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.2s both; }
  .filter-bar-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 32px; padding: 20px 0; }
  .filter-label { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .filter-tags { display: flex; gap: 0; list-style: none; }
  .filter-tags button { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.04em; color: var(--gray-500); background: none; border: none; padding: 6px 16px; cursor: pointer; position: relative; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .filter-tags button:hover { color: var(--ink); }
  .filter-tags button.active { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 500; }
  .filter-tags button.active::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -1px; left: 16px; right: 16px; height: 2px; background: var(--ink); }
  .article-list { padding: 0 48px; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.25s both; }
  .article-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .article-card { display: block; padding: 32px 28px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink); transition: background 0.2s; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); }
  .article-card:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid var(--stone); padding-left: 0; }
  .article-card:nth-child(even) { padding-right: 0; }
  .article-card:hover { background: var(--linen); }
  .article-card-image { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 3 / 4; background: var(--stone); margin-bottom: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 0.08em; overflow: hidden; }
  .article-card-pillar { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ember); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .article-card-title { font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: balance; }
  .article-card-excerpt { font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .article-card-meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .ad-slot { grid-column: 1 / -1; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--stone); padding: 40px 28px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; min-height: 200px; }
  .ad-slot-label { font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gray-400); border: 1px solid var(--stone); padding: 2px 8px; }
  .ad-slot-placeholder { width: 100%; max-width: 728px; height: 120px; background: var(--linen); border: 1px dashed var(--stone); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-400); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  .pagination { padding: 40px 48px; border-top: 1px solid var(--stone); display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 4px; animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both; }
  .pagination a, .pagination span { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-width: 40px; height: 40px; padding: 0 12px; font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-decoration: none; color: var(--gray-500); transition: color 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
  .pagination a:hover { color: var(--ink); background: var(--linen); }
  .pagination .active { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .pagination .ellipsis { color: var(--gray-400); cursor: default; min-width: 28px; }
  .pagination .prev, .pagination .next { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; gap: 6px; }
  .pagination .prev.disabled, .pagination .next.disabled { color: var(--stone); pointer-events: none; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header { padding: 40px 24px 36px; }
    .page-header-korean { font-size: 40px; }
    .page-header h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    .featured-article { padding: 0 24px; }
    .featured-article-title { font-size: 24px; }
    .filter-bar { padding: 0 24px; overflow-x: auto; -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch; }
    .filter-bar-inner { gap: 16px; min-width: max-content; }
    .filter-label { display: none; }
    .article-list { padding: 0 24px; }
    .article-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .article-card { border-right: none !important; padding-left: 0 !important; padding-right: 0 !important; }
    .article-card-title { font-size: 18px; }
    .ad-slot { padding: 32px 0; }
    .ad-slot-placeholder { height: 100px; }
    .pagination { padding: 32px 24px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .page-header-korean { font-size: 32px; }
    .page-header h1 { font-size: 26px; }
    .featured-article-title { font-size: 22px; }
  }
</style>
